---
import "../styles/main.css";
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no, viewport-fit=cover" />
  <title>Open-ClawBot — OpenClaw в Telegram за 1 минуту</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Премиальный запуск OpenClaw в Telegram за 1 минуту. Один тариф — 3 890 ₽/мес." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Onest:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#000000" />
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent" />
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="dark" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-noise"></div>

  <header class="header">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a class="brand" href="/"><img class="brand-logo" src="/assets/logo-bot.png" alt="logo"></a>
      <div class="row small-gap">
        <a class="btn header-btn header-btn--primary" href="/login/"><img class="header-btn__icon" src="/assets/icons/login/user-filled.svg" alt="">Войти</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <canvas id="heroDither" class="hero-dither" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
      <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="kicker">OpenClaw в Telegram · без SSH и Docker</p>
      <h1>Твой личный AI-ассистент<br>за 1 минуту</h1>
      <p class="lead">Один тариф <b>3 890 ₽/мес</b>. Включены VPS, установка, обновления и поддержка на русском.</p>
      <div class="stats">
        <div><strong>1 мин</strong><span>до запуска</span></div>
        <div><strong>1 тариф</strong><span>всё включено</span></div>
        <div><strong>24/7</strong><span>бот в онлайне</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#price">Запустить за 3 890 ₽</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#capabilities">Что умеет OpenClaw</a>
      </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel setup">
      <h2>Быстрая установка</h2>
      <p class="setup-subhead">Выбор модели на старте</p>
      <div class="model-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Выбор модели">
        <button class="model-tab active" data-model="claude" aria-selected="true"><img src="./assets/icons/claude.svg" alt="Claude"> Anthropic Claude</button>
        <button class="model-tab" data-model="gpt" aria-selected="false"><img src="./assets/icons/chatgpt.png" alt="GPT"> OpenAI ChatGPT</button>
        <button class="model-tab" data-model="gemini" aria-selected="false"><img src="./assets/icons/gemini.png" alt="Gemini"> Google Gemini</button>
        <button class="model-tab" data-model="deepseek" aria-selected="false"><img src="https://www.deepseek.com/favicon.ico" alt="DeepSeek"> DeepSeek</button>
      </div>
      <button class="more-ai-btn" id="moreAiBtn" type="button">Другие нейросети</button>
      <div class="more-ai-panel" id="moreAiPanel" aria-hidden="true">
        <button class="ai-option" data-model="mistral"><img src="https://mistral.ai/favicon.ico" alt="Mistral"> Mistral AI</button>
        <button class="ai-option" data-model="llama"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/meta/7ec6ff" alt="Llama"> Meta Llama</button>
        <button class="ai-option" data-model="cohere"><img src="https://cohere.com/favicon.ico" alt="Cohere"> Cohere</button>
        <button class="ai-option" data-model="qwen"><img src="https://chat.qwen.ai/favicon.ico" alt="Qwen"> Alibaba Qwen</button>
        <button class="ai-option" data-model="grok"><img src="https://grok.com/favicon.ico" alt="Grok"> xAI Grok</button>
      </div>
      <div class="model-info" id="modelInfo">
        <h3>Anthropic Claude</h3>
        <p>Максимум качества для сложных задач, кода и анализа.</p>
        <div class="model-pills" id="modelPills"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="setup-subhead channel-subhead">Настроить способ связи</p>
      <div class="channel-row">
        <button class="channel active" id="tgOpen"><img src="./assets/icons/telegram.png" alt="Telegram"> Telegram</button>
      </div>

      <div class="token-block">
        <p class="setup-subhead token-subhead">Выбрать количество токенов на старте</p>
        <div class="token-pills" id="tokenPills">
          <button class="token-pill active" type="button" data-value="1000">1000 ₽</button>
          <button class="token-pill" type="button" data-value="3000">3000 ₽</button>
          <button class="token-pill" type="button" data-value="5000">5000 ₽</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a class="btn btn-google full" href="#">Войти через Google</a>
      <p class="form-note">Вход нужен для запуска бота.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="modal-backdrop" id="tgModal" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="tgTitle">
        <button class="modal-close" id="tgClose" aria-label="Закрыть">×</button>
        <h3 id="tgTitle">Подключить Telegram</h3>
        <p class="modal-sub">Как получить токен бота?</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Откройте <b>@BotFather</b> в Telegram.</li>
          <li>Введите <code>/newbot</code> и создайте бота.</li>
          <li>Скопируйте токен и вставьте его ниже.</li>
        </ol>
        <label for="botToken">Введите токен бота</label>
        <input id="botToken" type="text" placeholder="1234567890:ABCdefGHI_jklMNOpqrSTUVwx" />
        <button class="btn btn-primary full" id="saveToken">Сохранить ✓</button>
      </div>
    </div>

